   588	
   589	## Algorithm — what the 3-trial experiment looks like across 5 processes
   590	
   591	```text
   592	harness
   593	  ├─> task-store-server (uvicorn, SqliteStore, shared_token=T)
   594	  │       bound to 127.0.0.1:$PORT after printing EDEN_TASK_STORE_LISTENING
   595	  ├─> planner-host  (StoreClient, ScriptedPlanner, worker-id=planner-1)
   596	  ├─> implementer-host (StoreClient, ScriptedImplementer, worker-id=implementer-1)
   597	  ├─> evaluator-host   (StoreClient, ScriptedEvaluator, worker-id=evaluator-1)
   598	  └─> orchestrator (StoreClient, Integrator, plan-tasks=plan-1,plan-2,plan-3)
   599	```
   600	
   601	1. Harness boots task-store-server, reads its port from stdout.
   602	2. Harness boots the 3 workers and orchestrator in parallel with the
   603	   URL and shared token. Each waits on readiness probe.
   604	3. Orchestrator seeds plan-1, plan-2, plan-3.
   605	4. Planner's next poll returns the 3 pending plan tasks. It claims
   606	   each, drafts `N` proposals (scripted), marks each ready, submits.
   607	5. Orchestrator's next iteration: finalizes plan tasks (accepts
   608	   each), dispatches an implement task per ready proposal.
   609	6. Implementer claims each, writes a real commit on
   610	   `refs/heads/work/<slug>-<trial_id>` in the shared bare repo via
   611	   `GitRepo`, creates a trial carrying that branch + SHA, and
   612	   submits `status=success`.
   613	7. Orchestrator accepts implement tasks, dispatches evaluate tasks.
   614	8. Evaluator claims each, submits metrics.
   615	9. Orchestrator accepts evaluate tasks (this also writes metrics on
   616	   the trial per the §2.2 composite commit). Trials are now
   617	   `success`.
   618	10. Orchestrator calls `Integrator.integrate(trial_id)` for each:
   619	    writes `refs/heads/trial/<id>-<slug>` via zero-oid CAS into the
   620	    bare repo, then `POST /trials/{id}/integrate` → store writes
   621	    `trial_commit_sha` + `trial.integrated` event.
   622	11. Next iteration finds no progress. Counter increments. After
   623	    `--max-quiescent-iterations` zero-progress iterations in a row,
   624	    orchestrator exits 0.
   625	12. Harness observes the exit, asserts DB + repo state, SIGTERMs the
   626	    workers + task-store-server, waits for them, tears down temp
   627	    dirs.
   628	
